Get parameter values from calibration results

Source: R/get_param.R
get_param.Rd

Get parameter values from calibration results

Usage

get_param(calib, na_value, fit_col = "fit", best = FALSE)

Arguments

calib

A list with the calibration results loaded using read_calib.

na_value

A numeric value which corresponds to the NA value used in the calibration.

fit_col

character; name of column containing fit values. Default is "fit".

best

A logical value indicating whether to return the best parameter values or all parameter values.

Value

A data frame with the parameter values.
